OL,3,CTerror attack survivors face rising
OL,4,Conline abuse and death threats, report
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FOne of the report's co-authors,
OL,8,FClaudia Vince, a survivor of the
OL,9,FFishmongers' Hall attack on November
OL,10,F29, 2019, has urged the Government to
OL,11,Famend the Online Safety Act.
OL,13,FIn the attack, five people were
OL,14,Fstabbed in central London, two of them
OL,15,Ffatally.
OL,17,FThe attacker, Usman Khan, had been
OL,18,Freleased on licence in 2018 after
OL,19,Fserving a sentence for terrorist
OL,20,Foffences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
