OL,3,CTerror attack survivors face rising
OL,4,Conline abuse and death threats, report
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"These harms can be stopped ` and we
OL,8,Fall have a part to play. Ministers
OL,9,Fshould amend the Online Safety Act to
OL,10,Fensure minimum standards at social
OL,11,Fmedia companies," she said.
OL,13,FVince added that the UK's media
OL,14,Fwatchdog, Ofcom, "seems asleep at the
OL,15,Fwheel" when it comes to enforcing
OL,16,Frules on social media companies.
