OL,3,CTerror attack survivors face rising
OL,4,Conline abuse and death threats, report
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"Social media companies who are
OL,8,Fprofiting from the abuse on their
OL,9,Fplatform need to fundamentally change
OL,10,Ftheir approach and provide the
OL,11,Fprotections they often already promise
OL,12,Fin their own terms and conditions,"
OL,13,Fshe added.
OL,15,F"Finally, all of us need to ensure we
OL,16,Fare part of the solution, not part of
OL,17,Fthe problem ` that means no sharing of
OL,18,Fharmful content, no engaging with
OL,19,Ftoxic influencers, and sticking to
OL,20,Fofficial web pages for helpful advice
OL,21,Fwhen needed."
