OL,7,FVince also told ITV News she struggled
OL,8,Fto cope with videos of the
OL,9,FFishmongers' Hall attack being widely
OL,10,Freshared on social media.
OL,12,F"I think what we found after
OL,13,FFishmongers was the footage of the
OL,14,Fattack was shared really, really
OL,15,Fwidely within hours of the attack
OL,16,Fhappening," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
