OL,3,CTerror attack survivors face rising
OL,4,Conline abuse and death threats, report
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"So before we even knew what had
OL,8,Fhappened, there was hundreds of angles
OL,9,Fof the same footage being shared on
OL,10,Fsocial media. And that was really hard
OL,11,Fto manage.
OL,13,F"It's a time when your mental health
OL,14,Fand going through such a trauma is
OL,15,Falready kind of completely flipped
OL,16,Fupside down. Your whole life has been
OL,17,Fflipped upside down. And it does feel
OL,18,Flike it exacerbates lots of those
OL,19,Fconcerns and anxieties."
