OL,3,CTerror attack survivors face rising
OL,4,Conline abuse and death threats, report
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FAn Ofcom spokesperson said: "We know
OL,8,Fthe devastating impact that online
OL,9,Fabuse can have. Duties on tech firms
OL,10,Funder the Online Safety Act started
OL,11,Fcoming into force this year, after
OL,12,Fthis research was carried out
OL,14,F"Platforms must now take appropriate
OL,15,Fsteps to protect UK users, and we've
OL,16,Fshown we'll take enforcement action if
OL,17,Fevidence suggests companies are
OL,18,Ffailing to comply. We've launched
OL,19,Finvestigations into over 90 sites and
OL,20,Fapps, and will be providing updates on
OL,21,Four work in the coming weeks."
